<h1 class='doclevel'>17.Test Suite : amir3468_BBT</h1>
<div><p>Se testeaza F01</p>
</div><a name="toc_tc28843"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P231-95: ECP - Valid&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">amir3468</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>Se verifica faptul ca sistemul permite adaugarea unui produs nou atunci cand toate atributele introduse sunt valide si complete.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Preconditions:</span><br /><p>- Nu exista deja in sistem un produs cu acelasi id</p>

<p>- Baza de date este disponibila</p>
</td></tr><tr><td><span class="label">#:</span></td><td><span class="label">Step actions:</span></td><td><span class="label">Expected Results:</span></td></tr><tr><td width="5">1</td><td><p>Se acceseaza functionalitatea addPrduct():<br />
- se introduc&nbsp;valorile atributelor id, nume, pret, ...</p>

<p>- se apasa butonul Add</p>
</td><td><p>Produsul este adaugat cu succes.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Execution type:</span></td><td colspan="3">Manual</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Estimated exec. duration (min):</span></td><td colspan="3">2.00</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Importance:</span></td><td colspan="3">Medium</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"></td></tr><tr><td > name of the autotest class:</td><td  colspan = "3" >ProductTest</td></tr>
